Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration", ko="협조자"}, "It has come to my attention that some have lately called me a collaborator, as if such a term were shameful.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration01.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration2", ko="협조자2"}, "I ask you, what greater endeavor exists than that of collaboration?", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration02.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration3", ko="협조자3"}, "In our current unparalleled enterprise, refusal to collaborate is simply a refusal to grow--an insistence on suicide, if you will.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration03.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration4", ko="협조자4"}, "Did the lungfish refuse to breathe air? It did not.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration04.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration5", ko="협조자5"}, "It crept forth boldly while its brethren remained in the blackest ocean abyss, with lidless eyes forever staring at the dark, ignorant and doomed despite their eternal vigilance.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration05.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration6", ko="협조자6"}, "Would we model ourselves on the trilobite?", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration06.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration7", ko="협조자7"}, "Are all the accomplishments of humanity fated to be nothing more than a layer of broken plastic shards thinly strewn across a fossil bed, sandwiched between the Burgess shale and an eon's worth of mud?", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration07.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration8", ko="협조자8"}, "In order to be true to our nature, and our destiny, we must aspire to greater things. We have outgrown our cradle. It is futile to cry for mother's milk, when our true sustenance awaits us among the stars.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration08.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration9", ko="협조자9"}, "And only the universal union that small minds call 'The Combine' can carry us there.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration09.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration10", ko="협조자10"}, "Therefore I say, yes, I am a collaborator. We must all collaborate, willingly, eagerly, if we expect to reap the benefits of unification.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration10.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="collaboration11", ko="협조자11"}, "And reap we shall.", "vo/breencast/br_collaboration11.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct", ko="본능"}, "Let me read a letter I recently received. \"Dear Dr. Breen. Why has the Combine seen fit to suppress our reproductive cycle? Sincerely, A Concerned Citizen.\"", "vo/breencast/br_instinct01.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct2", ko="본능2"}, "Thank you for writing, Concerned. Of course, your question touches on one of the most basic biological impulses, with all its associated hopes and fears for the future of the species.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct02.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct3", ko="본능3"}, "I also detect some unspoken questions. Do our benefactors really know what's best for us? What gives them the right to make this kind of decision for mankind? Will they ever deactivate the suppression field and let us breed again?", "vo/breencast/br_instinct03.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct4", ko="본능4"}, "Allow me to address the anxieties underlying your concerns, rather than try to answer every possible question you might have left unvoiced.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct04.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct5", ko="본능5"}, "First, let us consider the fact that for the first time ever, as a species, immortality is in our reach.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct05.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct6", ko="본능6"}, "This simple fact has far-reaching implications. It requires radical rethinking and revision of our genetic imperatives.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct06.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct7", ko="본능7"}, "It also requires planning and forethought that run in direct opposition to our neural pre-sets.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct07.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct8", ko="본능8"}, "I find it helpful at times like these to remind myself that our true enemy is Instinct.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct08.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct9", ko="본능9"}, "Instinct was our mother when we were an infant species.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct09.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct10", ko="본능10"}, "Instinct coddled us and kept us safe in those hardscrabble years when we hardened our sticks and cooked our first meals above a meager fire", "vo/breencast/br_instinct10.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct11", ko="본능11"}, "and startled at the shadows that leapt upon the cavern's walls.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct11.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct12", ko="본능12"}, "But inseparable from Instinct is its dark twin, Superstition.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct12.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct13", ko="본능13"}, "Instinct is inextricably bound to unreasoning impulses, and today we clearly see its true nature. Instinct has just become aware of its irrelevance, and like a cornered beast, it will not go down without a bloody fight.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct13.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct14", ko="본능14"}, "Instinct would inflict a fatal injury on our species.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct14.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct15", ko="본능15"}, "Instinct creates its own oppressors, and bids us rise up against them.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct15.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct16", ko="본능16"}, "Instinct tells us that the unknown is a threat, rather than an opportunity.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct16.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct17", ko="본능17"}, "Instinct slyly and covertly compels us away from change and progress.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct17.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct18", ko="본능18"}, "Instinct, therefore, must be expunged.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct18.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct19", ko="본능19"}, "It must be fought tooth and nail, beginning with the basest of human urges: The urge to reproduce.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct19.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct20", ko="본능20"}, "We should thank our benefactors for giving us respite from this overpowering force.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct20.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct21", ko="본능21"}, "They have thrown a switch and exorcised our demons in a single stroke.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct21.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct22", ko="본능22"}, "They have given us the strength we never could have summoned to overcome this compulsion.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct22.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct23", ko="본능23"}, "They have given us purpose. They have turned our eyes toward the stars.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct23.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct24", ko="본능24"}, "Let me assure you that the suppressing field will be shut off on the day that we have mastered ourselves...the day we can prove we no longer need it.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct24.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="instinct25", ko="본능25"}, "And that day of transformation, I have it on good authority, is close at hand.", "vo/breencast/br_instinct25.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome", ko="환영"}, "Welcome. Welcome to City 17.", "vo/breencast/br_welcome01.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome2", ko="환영2"}, "You have chosen, or been chosen, to relocate to one of our finest remaining urban centers.", "vo/breencast/br_welcome02.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome3", ko="환영3"}, "I thought so much of City 17 that I elected to establish my Administration here, in the Citadel so thoughtfully provided by Our Benefactors.", "vo/breencast/br_welcome03.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome4", ko="환영4"}, "I have been proud to call City 17 my home.", "vo/breencast/br_welcome04.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome5", ko="환영5"}, "And so, whether you are here to stay, or passing through on your way to parts unknown,", "vo/breencast/br_welcome05.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome6", ko="환영6"}, "Welcome to City 17.", "vo/breencast/br_welcome06.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", {en="welcome7", ko="환영7"}, "It's safer here.", "vo/breencast/br_welcome07.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor", ko = "질서파괴"}, "We now have direct confirmation of a disruptor in our midst, one who has acquired an almost messianic reputation in the minds of certain citizens.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor01.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor2", ko = "질서파괴2"}, "His figure is synonymous with the darkest urges of instinct, ignorance and decay. Some of the worst excesses of the Black Mesa Incident have been laid directly at his feet.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor02.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor3", ko = "질서파괴3"}, "And yet unsophisticated minds continue to imbue him with romantic power, giving him such dangerous poetic labels as the One Free Man, the Opener of the Way.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor03.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor4", ko = "질서파괴4"}, "Let me remind all citizens of the dangers of magical thinking.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor04.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor5", ko = "질서파괴5"}, "We have scarcely begun to climb from the dark pit of our species' evolution. Let us not slide backward into oblivion, just as we have finally begun to see the light.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor05.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor6", ko = "질서파괴6"}, "If you see this so-called Free Man, report him.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor06.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor7", ko = "질서파괴7"}, "Civic deeds do not go unrewarded. And contrariwise, complicity with his cause will not go unpunished.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor07.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "distruptor8", ko = "질서파괴8"}, "Be wise. Be safe. Be aware.", "vo/breencast/br_distruptor08.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch", ko = "감시부대"}, "I have been asked to say a few words to the transhuman arm of Sector Seventeen Overwatch, concerning recent successes in containing members of the resistance Science Team.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch01.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch2", ko = "감시부대2"}, "Let me say up front that I regret having to temper my heartfelt congratulations with a strong measure of disappointment. But I wouldn't be doing my duty as your Administrator if I didn't pass along the message I have received from Our Benefactors.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch02.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch3", ko = "감시부대3"}, "The capture of Eli Vance is an event of major significance, make no mistake. And while it's true that conceivably we could have taken him at almost any time in the last several years, the manner of his capture may prove to have unexpected benefits.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch03.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch4", ko = "감시부대4"}, "It cannot have gone unnoticed by all resistance members that Doctor Vance's capture coincided with the act of giving shelter to Gordon Freeman. This might cause other resistance members to think twice before harbouring Doctor Freeman. It might cause them to question his allegiance; even prompt some to turn him out, or turn him over to our cause.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch04.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch5", ko = "감시부대5"}, "However, we cannot count on such developments. Doctor Freeman's reputation is such that other desperate renegades are likely to grant him a great deal of license in the spirit of spreading general chaos and terror.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch05.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch6", ko = "감시부대6"}, "This brings me to the one note of disappointment I must echo from our Benefactors. Obviously I am not on the ground to closely command or second-guess the dedicated forces of the Overwatch, but this does not mean I can shirk responsibility for recent lapses and even outright failures on their part. I have been severely questioned about these shortcomings, and now must put the question to you.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch06.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch7", ko = "감시부대7"}, "How could one man have slipped through your force's fingers time and time again? How is it possible? This is not some agent provocateur or highly trained assassin we are discussing. Gordon Freeman is a theoretical physicist who had hardly earned the distinction of his Ph.D. at the time of the Black Mesa Incident. I have good reason to believe that in the intervening years, he was in a state that precluded further development of covert skills. The man you have consistently failed to slow, let alone capture, is by all standards simply that--an ordinary man. How can you have failed to apprehend him?", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch07.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch8", ko = "감시부대8"}, "Well...I will leave the upbraiding for another time, to the extent it proves necessary. Now is the moment to redeem yourselves. If the transhuman forces are to prove themselves an indispensable augmentation to the Combine Overwatch, they will have to earn the privilege. I'm sure I don't have to remind you that the alternative, if you can call it that, is total extinction - in union with all the other unworthy branches of the species.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch08.wav", true)
Schema.voices.Add("Breencast", { en = "overwatch9", ko = "감시부대9"}, "Let's not allow it to come to that. I have done my best to convince Our Benefactors that you are the finest the species has to offer. So far they have accepted my argument, but without concrete evidence to back it up, my words sound increasingly hollow even to me. The burden of proof is on you. As is the consequence of failure. I'll just leave it at that.", "vo/breencast/br_overwatch09.wav", true)

